description:
Workshop Wednesdays provide anyone with an interest in programming, data and web development an opportunity to advance their skills and knowledge in person.

This week we're running our ever popular [Python Code Dojo](https://www.meetup.com/codehub-bristol/events/296409140/), a non-competitive, mixed group coding session, where people of all levels are welcome.

Alternatively, if you just want to use the opportunity to study, have a chat with like-minded people, or perhaps you seek feedback on your ideas or just interested in socialising with people from the technology industry, come and hang out with us.

Our eternal gratitude goes to [Womens Tech Hub](https://www.wthub.org/) for organising and making this happen.
title: CodeHub @WorkshopWednesdays
